Flow.description: Checks the 'To:' field when an Email Message record is created (email comes in attached to a case). If the 'To:' field matches any of the email addresses in the Process Builder, it assigns the DC code to the 'Incoming Email DC' field on the case. This is then picked up by the 'Case Reassignment Part 2 - Flow Launch' Process Builder.
Flow.label: Case - Case Reassignment Part 1 - Email Address Check
